 Blank guns are frequently modified to fire projectiles. For this reason also blank cartridges are altered by adding self-made projectiles. Depending on the modification self-made guns are comparable with "real" guns concerning the technical effects and wound ballistic data. We report about fatalities due to manipulated blank guns and blank cartridges. The autopsy findings as well as the weapons are described. A short overview of the German weapons law concerning altered weapons is given.  
